p: Henan, Yunnan and Guangdong Provinces had dengue outbreaks in 2013. Full E-gene sequences of dengue virus detected in these Provinces in 2013 were downloaded from GenBank (As of August 25 th 2015) ( S1 Table). The sequences detected in China were compared with published sequences by using the nucleotide blast program in the NCBI.
